@host = http://localhost:5000

### Listar cardápio
GET {{host}}/api/menu
Accept: application/json

###

### Criar pedido — combo completo (20% desconto)
POST {{host}}/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customer": "Mesa 01",
  "note": "",
  "items": [
    "11111111-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
    "11111111-0000-0000-0000-000000000004",
    "11111111-0000-0000-0000-000000000005"
  ]
}

###

### Criar pedido — sanduíche + refrigerante (15% desconto)
POST {{host}}/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customer": "Balcão",
  "note": "sem gelo",
  "items": [
    "11111111-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
    "11111111-0000-0000-0000-000000000005"
  ]
}

###

### Criar pedido — sanduíche + batata (10% desconto)
POST {{host}}/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customer": "Delivery",
  "note": "",
  "items": [
    "11111111-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
    "11111111-0000-0000-0000-000000000004"
  ]
}

###

### Listar todos os pedidos
GET {{host}}/api/orders
Accept: application/json

###

### Buscar pedido por ID (substituir pelo ID retornado no POST)
GET {{host}}/api/orders/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Accept: application/json

###

### Atualizar pedido (substituir pelo ID retornado no POST)
PUT {{host}}/api/orders/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customer": "Mesa 01",
  "note": "sem cebola",
  "items": [
    "11111111-0000-0000-0000-000000000003"
  ]
}

###

### Remover pedido (substituir pelo ID retornado no POST)
DELETE {{host}}/api/orders/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000

###

### Erro — categoria duplicada
POST {{host}}/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customer": "Teste",
  "note": "",
  "items": [
    "11111111-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
    "11111111-0000-0000-0000-000000000002"
  ]
}

###
